Smoke Test logic

	How to trigger your Smoke Test?

		CI/CD:

			This stands for - Continues Integration/Continues Delivery and Continues Development.

				Examples of CI/CD:

					Jenkins
					Bamboo,
					TravisCI
					GitLab
					TimCity

			We will be using Jenkins, as it is the most popular

	Jenkins:

		Jenkins is a CI/CD that can automatically execute your tests based on some triggers.

			Trigger examples:

				Periodically:

					Every morning
					Every hour

				After deployment:

					A new build was deployed to the test environment, smoke test must be triggered automatically without human intervention.
